steps.description:
To properly cut your pineapple, cut off the crown and the base of the fruit. Place the pineapple upright on a cutting board and carefully slice on the inside of the rind from top to bottom. Make sure to cut deep enough to remove all of the prickly rind. The pineapple will still have its "eyes" at this point. You can cut them away individually, but it might be easier to cut along the sides of the pineapple in a diagonal, v-shaped trench since the eyes should be patterned along the sides in a diagonal. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/23/Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-11.jpg/v4-459px-Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-11.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/2/23/Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-11.jpg/v4-759px-Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-11.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Cut the pineapple in half lengthwise and then in half again so that you have four triangle-shaped quarters. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c5/Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-13Bullet1.jpg/v4-459px-Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-13Bullet1.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/c/c5/Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-13Bullet1.jpg/v4-759px-Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-13Bullet1.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}

Cut the tough core out of the center and discard, then slice the four pieces into chunks or slices. {"smallUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/59/Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-13Bullet2.jpg/v4-459px-Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-13Bullet2.jpg","bigUrl":"https://www.wikihow.com/images/thumb/5/59/Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-13Bullet2.jpg/v4-759px-Tell-if-a-Pineapple-Is-Ripe-Step-13Bullet2.jpg","smallWidth":460,"smallHeight":306,"bigWidth":760,"bigHeight":506.31868131868134,"licensing":"<div class="mw-parser-output"><p>License: <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/3.0/">Creative Commons</a><br>
</p><p><br />
</p></div>"}
